 13:20):[/b]<br/><br/>铜箔这鱼尾有点长[/quote]<br/>你知道我为什么分享怎么卖 国算 铜箔  电池 半导体的方法了么<br/>这种方法你平时绝对看不见有人说", "lou": 2377, "content_length": 87, "reply_to": 866480433, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777526637}, {"pid": 866481720, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 39, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-30 13:31", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们自己看啊  白线在退<br/>我已经和你们说过了 这波是机构诱多  早上科技+券商快速放量突破压力位 如果不是知道诱多  大家肯定冲进去了<br/>我可是提前告诉你们了", "lou": 2378, "content_length": 135, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777527067}, {"pid": 866482036, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 18, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-30 13:33", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=866481887,45974302,4606]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=62771233]极地丶之光[/uid] (2026-04-30 13:32):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，现在是维持机构节后继续诱多还是这波已经结束，机构开始出货了？[/quote]<br/>是出货 但是不是搞坏市场那种 也就是这里利用诱多做个T。不是坏事 一", "lou": 2379, "content_length": 66, "reply_to": 866481887, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1777527224}], "__T": {"fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "topic_misc": null, "subject": "自立自强，科学技术打头阵", "locked": 0, "recommend": 0, "quote_to": null, "quote_from": 0, "type": 36, "replies": 155491, "authorid": 150058, "postdate": 1768179906, "lastpost": 1782109336, "jdata": null, "author": "-阿狼-", "lastposter": "米璐璐6666LLL", "digest": 0, "lastmodify": 1782109344, "tpid": 0, "post_misc_var": {"content_length": 412, "fid": 706, "comment_id": ",854270755,860174433", "14": {"17": 1, "14": 4, "13": 4, "12": 1}, "16": "63335896,19412700,26652007,67067074,20672033,66881586,67068843,66199622,60819388,60409766,67057614,60264977,61082281,42701832,66998841,61574956,61272875,67082978,66949654,65530601,60630412,60240136,66038632,63481990,61973100,60192597,66985104,19043499,39108806,41714633,7046671,65647302,40696141,3481707,654677,39235785,66063392,39314790,67071606,66251279,42126891,61602239,4785041,42995612,67024